  "detailed_description": "Sippy Disco is a relaxing game where you light up disco tiles to complete each dance floor. As the game progresses, you will encounter different tiles and characters that can both help and hinder your progress. The fewer moves you make, the higher your score.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/d57d1c3f06f6fef36f7f95b7bd3d7ebf.poster.avif?t=1717538749\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/d57d1c3f06f6fef36f7f95b7bd3d7ebf.webm?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/d57d1c3f06f6fef36f7f95b7bd3d7ebf.mp4?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customize your unicorn<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/027e13a9b9c411e474413c5a477932d3.poster.avif?t=1717538749\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/027e13a9b9c411e474413c5a477932d3.webm?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/027e13a9b9c411e474413c5a477932d3.mp4?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Unwind by lighting up the dance floor in a stress-free environment<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/ce2b58aa1289f269187f167c1d77e384.poster.avif?t=1717538749\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/ce2b58aa1289f269187f167c1d77e384.webm?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/ce2b58aa1289f269187f167c1d77e384.mp4?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Chill with a groovy disco soundtrack<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/8b63135c7bee02cbb3209cf8e5f7297b.poster.avif?t=1717538749\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/8b63135c7bee02cbb3209cf8e5f7297b.webm?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/8b63135c7bee02cbb3209cf8e5f7297b.mp4?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Be inspired by inspirational quotes from Sippy the Unicorn<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/d3a40f71a86d9647d49f1ec57d0f531d.poster.avif?t=1717538749\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/d3a40f71a86d9647d49f1ec57d0f531d.webm?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/d3a40f71a86d9647d49f1ec57d0f531d.mp4?t=1717538749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766470/extras/b475b451f58ff0d67845c3459d32550b.poster.avif?t=1717538749\" width=314 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.